          `${kw('type')} ${tp('Middleware')}      = (cmd${op(':')} ${kw('unknown')}, next${op(':')} () => ${tp('Promise')}&lt;${kw('unknown')}&gt;) => ${tp('Promise')}&lt;${kw('unknown')}&gt;;`,
          '',
          `${kw('export class')} ${tp('CommandBus')} {`,
          `  ${kw('private')} handlers    = ${kw('new')} ${fn('Map')}&lt;${tp('string')}, ${tp('Handler')}&lt;${kw('unknown')}, ${kw('unknown')}&gt;&gt;();`,
          `  ${kw('private')} middlewares${op(':')} ${tp('Middleware')}[] = [];`,
          '',
          `  ${fn('register')}&lt;T, R&gt;(name${op(':')} ${tp('string')}, h${op(':')} ${tp('Handler')}&lt;T, R&gt;)${op(':')} ${kw('void')} {`,
          `    ${kw('this')}.handlers.${fn('set')}(name, h ${kw('as')} ${tp('Handler')}&lt;${kw('unknown')}, ${kw('unknown')}&gt;);`,
          `  }`,
          '',
          `  ${fn('use')}(mw${op(':')} ${tp('Middleware')})${op(':')} ${kw('void')} { ${kw('this')}.middlewares.${fn('push')}(mw); }`,
          '',
          `  ${kw('async')} ${fn('dispatch')}&lt;R&gt;(name${op(':')} ${tp('string')}, cmd${op(':')} ${kw('unknown')})${op(':')} ${tp('Promise')}&lt;R&gt; {`,
          `    ${kw('const')} handler = ${kw('this')}.handlers.${fn('get')}(name);`,
          `    ${kw('if')} (!handler) ${kw('throw new')} ${fn('Error')}(${st('`No handler registered: ${name}`')});`,
          `    ${kw('const')} chain = ${kw('this')}.middlewares.${fn('reduceRight')}(`,
          `      (next, mw) => () => mw(cmd, next),`,
          `      () => handler(cmd),`,
          `    );`,
          `    ${kw('return')} chain() ${kw('as')} ${tp('Promise')}&lt;R&gt;;`,
          `  }`,
          `}`,
        ].join('\n'),
